{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":1480,"text":"I am holding something remarkably old."},{"time":4440,"text":"It is older than any human artifact,"},{"time":7440,"text":"older than life on Earth,"},{"time":9760,"text":"older than the continents\nand the oceans between them."},{"time":13520,"text":"This was formed\nover four billion years ago"},{"time":16640,"text":"in the earliest days of the solar system"},{"time":18800,"text":"while the planets were still forming."},{"time":21160,"text":"This rusty lump of nickel and iron\nmay not appear special,"},{"time":24520,"text":"but when it is cut open ..."},{"time":28320,"text":"you can see that it is different\nfrom earthly metals."},{"time":31440,"text":"This pattern reveals metallic crystals\nthat can only form out in space"},{"time":35360,"text":"where molten metal\ncan cool extremely slowly,"},{"time":37960,"text":"a few degrees every million years."},{"time":40760,"text":"This was once part\nof a much larger object,"},{"time":43280,"text":"one of millions left over\nafter the planets formed."},{"time":45880,"text":"We call these objects asteroids."}]},{"cues":[{"time":49160,"text":"Asteroids are our oldest\nand most numerous cosmic neighbors."},{"time":52960,"text":"This graphic shows near-Earth asteroids\norbiting around the Sun,"},{"time":56040,"text":"shown in yellow,"},{"time":57320,"text":"and swinging close to the Earth's orbit,"},{"time":59280,"text":"shown in blue."},{"time":60520,"text":"The sizes of the Earth, Sun and asteroids\nhave been greatly exaggerated"},{"time":63880,"text":"so you can see them clearly."},{"time":65280,"text":"Teams of scientists across the globe\nare searching for these objects,"},{"time":68680,"text":"discovering new ones every day,"},{"time":70640,"text":"steadily mapping near-Earth space."},{"time":73440,"text":"Much of this work is funded by NASA."},{"time":75760,"text":"I think of the search for these asteroids\nas a giant public works project,"},{"time":79560,"text":"but instead of building a highway,\nwe're charting outer space,"},{"time":82840,"text":"building an archive\nthat will last for generations."}]},{"cues":[{"time":85840,"text":"These are the 1,556 near-Earth asteroids\ndiscovered just last year."},{"time":93800,"text":"And these are all of the known\nnear-Earth asteroids,"},{"time":97360,"text":"which at last count was 13,733."},{"time":101400,"text":"Each one has been imaged, cataloged"},{"time":103560,"text":"and had its path\naround the Sun determined."},{"time":105960,"text":"Although it varies\nfrom asteroid to asteroid,"},{"time":108080,"text":"the paths of most asteroids\ncan be predicted for dozens of years."},{"time":111360,"text":"And the paths of some asteroids can be\npredicted with incredible precision."},{"time":115160,"text":"For example, scientists\nat the Jet Propulsion Laboratory"},{"time":117840,"text":"predicted where the asteroid Toutatis\nwas going to be four years in advance"},{"time":121880,"text":"to within 30 kilometers."},{"time":124000,"text":"In those four years,"},{"time":125320,"text":"Toutatis traveled 8.5 billion kilometers."},{"time":129160,"text":"That's a fractional precision"},{"time":130759,"text":"of 0.000000004."}]},{"cues":[{"time":139960,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":142480,"text":"Now, the reason I have\nthis beautiful asteroid fragment"},{"time":145160,"text":"is because, like all neighbors,"},{"time":146720,"text":"asteroids sometimes drop by unexpectedly."}]},{"cues":[{"time":149400,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":152520,"text":"Three years ago today,"},{"time":154160,"text":"a small asteroid exploded\nover the city of Chelyabinsk, Russia."},{"time":157840,"text":"That object was about 19 meters across,"},{"time":160160,"text":"or about as big as a convenience store."},{"time":162840,"text":"Objects of this size hit the Earth\nevery 50 years or so."}]},{"cues":[{"time":167720,"text":"66 million years ago,"},{"time":169600,"text":"a much larger object hit the Earth,"},{"time":171560,"text":"causing a massive extinction."},{"time":173360,"text":"75 percent of plant\nand animal species were lost,"},{"time":176600,"text":"including, sadly, the dinosaurs."},{"time":179320,"text":"That object was\nabout 10 kilometers across,"},{"time":182040,"text":"and 10 kilometers is roughly\nthe cruising altitude of a 747 jet."},{"time":186240,"text":"So the next time you're in an airplane,"},{"time":188160,"text":"snag a window seat, look out\nand imagine a rock so enormous"},{"time":192000,"text":"that resting on the ground,"},{"time":194120,"text":"it just grazes your wingtip."},{"time":196880,"text":"It's so wide that it takes your plane\none full minute to fly past it."},{"time":201278,"text":"That's the size of the asteroid\nthat hit the Earth."}]},{"cues":[{"time":204518,"text":"It has only been within my lifetime"},{"time":206318,"text":"that asteroids have been considered\na credible threat to our planet."},{"time":209558,"text":"And since then, there's been\na focused effort underway"},{"time":212158,"text":"to discover and catalog these objects."},{"time":215238,"text":"I am lucky enough\nto be part of this effort."},{"time":217358,"text":"I'm part of a team of scientists\nthat use NASA's NEOWISE telescope."},{"time":221038,"text":"Now, NEOWISE was not\ndesigned to find asteroids."},{"time":223758,"text":"It was designed to orbit the earth\nand look far beyond our solar system"},{"time":227998,"text":"to seek out the coldest stars\nand the most luminous galaxies."},{"time":231438,"text":"And it did that very well\nfor its designed lifetime of seven months."},{"time":235518,"text":"But today, six years later,\nit's still going."},{"time":238798,"text":"We've repurposed it\nto discover and study asteroids."},{"time":241558,"text":"And although it's\na wonderful little space robot,"},{"time":243918,"text":"these days it's kind of like a used car."},{"time":246518,"text":"The cryogen that used to refrigerate\nits sensors is long gone,"},{"time":249798,"text":"so we joke that\nits air-conditioning is broken."},{"time":252478,"text":"It's got 920 million miles\non the odometer,"},{"time":256918,"text":"but it still runs great"},{"time":258198,"text":"and reliably takes a photograph\nof the sky every 11 seconds."},{"time":261798,"text":"It's taken 23 photos\nsince I began speaking to you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":266118,"text":"One of the reasons NEOWISE is so valuable"},{"time":268318,"text":"is that it sees the sky\nin the thermal infrared."},{"time":270958,"text":"That means that instead of seeing\nthe sunlight that asteroids reflect,"},{"time":274318,"text":"NEOWISE sees the heat that they emit."},{"time":276158,"text":"This is a vital capability\nsince some asteroids are as dark as coal"},{"time":279918,"text":"and can be difficult or impossible\nto spot with other telescopes."},{"time":283398,"text":"But all asteroids, light or dark,\nshine brightly for NEOWISE."}]},{"cues":[{"time":288958,"text":"Astronomers are using\nevery technique at their disposal"},{"time":291758,"text":"to discover and study asteroids."},{"time":294078,"text":"In 2010, a historic milestone was reached."},{"time":296958,"text":"The community, together, discovered\nover 90 percent of asteroids"},{"time":301038,"text":"bigger than one kilometer across --"},{"time":302918,"text":"objects capable\nof massive destruction to Earth."},{"time":305918,"text":"But the job's not done yet."},{"time":307518,"text":"An object 140 meters or bigger\ncould decimate a medium-sized country."},{"time":312478,"text":"So far, we've only found\n25 percent of those."}]},{"cues":[{"time":316238,"text":"We must keep searching the sky\nfor near-Earth asteroids."},{"time":319678,"text":"We are the only species\nable to understand calculus"},{"time":322438,"text":"or build telescopes."},{"time":324118,"text":"We know how to find these objects."},{"time":326118,"text":"This is our responsibility."},{"time":328278,"text":"If we found a hazardous asteroid\nwith significant early warning,"},{"time":332078,"text":"we could nudge it out of the way."},{"time":333798,"text":"Unlike earthquakes, hurricanes\nor volcanic eruptions,"},{"time":336878,"text":"an asteroid impact\ncan be precisely predicted"},{"time":339798,"text":"and prevented."},{"time":341278,"text":"What we need to do now\nis map near-Earth space."},{"time":344438,"text":"We must keep searching the sky."}]},{"cues":[{"time":346318,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":347558,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}